Corporate Lawyer, Dubai, 0-3PQE
Corporate Lawyer, Dubai, 0-3PQE
Location:  --Dubai
This top tier global law firm is looking for a junior corporate lawyer to join their leading team in Dubai. They advise on some of the most innovative and complex transactions in the region, which is the result of many years’ experience in The Middle East.
The ideal candidate will be a bright, junior corporate lawyer with experience gained from a top tier international law firm. You will be a common law qualified lawyer with a strong academic background. You will also have experience in or be keen to work in Funds / Real Estate / Regulatory. Middle East experience is preferred, but not essential.
The firm has a strong presence across the Middle East with expertise in high profile, multi-jurisdictional transactions. The team in Dubai advises on general corporate and corporate finance work, including international equity offerings, IPOs, joint ventures, private equity work and cross-border mergers and acquisitions.
